room_title: Escape room "Cell Block 4 Death Row" by OB-Xscape Rooms in Southern Shores
room_address: 1 Ocean Boulevard  Suite 109 Southern Shores, NC 27949
room_description:
You have been locked up and on death row, for a crime, you were wrongfully convicted 22 years ago. The guards are off the Cell Block attending to an unexpected emergency which caused the lights to go out.
You and the other Cell Block 4 inmates are left alone on an honor system that you all will continue to follow protocol. You are set to be executed in a week, so what do you have to lose? You have 60 minutes until the lights are restored back on to escape or you will die trying.
